<h4 class="text-center">
  ILM APP is a web application for using <span class="text-danger"><b>Ivy Lee Method</b></span>.
  You can use it by signing up.
</h4>
<h1>What is Ivy Lee Method ?</h1>
<h4 class="text-center">
  Ivy Lee Method is <span class="text-danger">an efficient way to write to-do lists</span>.
</h4>
<h1>How to use ILM APP ?</h1>
<ol class="h4">
  <li>Fill in 6 things to do tomorrow</li>
  <li>Next day, proceed with work and study along the ILM APP</li>
  <li>Forget what you couldn't do without regret</li>
  <li>On that night, fill in 6 items for tomorrow</li>
  <li>Do these every day</li>
</ol>
<h1>What is the effect ?</h1>
<h4 class="text-center">Too many choices will spend a lot of energy on decision making</h4>
<h3 class="text-center">Reduce the number of decisions</h3>
